      "value": "<p>Life-preserving energy radiates from you in an aura with a 30-foot radius. Until the spell ends, the aura moves with you, centered on you. Each nonhostile creature in the aura (including you) has resistance to necrotic damage, and its hit point maximum can't be reduced. In addition, at the end of each of your turns, all nonhostile, living creatures in the aura with 0 hit points regain 1 hit point.</p>",
